Class:        Mammalia
Habitat:      Savanna
Diet:         Carnivore
Lifespan:     11 years
Weight:       30 kg
Status:       Endangered
Fact:         80% hunting success rate; votes on hunts by sneezing democratically

Name:         Cheetah
Scientific:   Acinonyx jubatus
